Don&#39;t mind if your opponent double, your shadow is able to kill a lots of deck!<br />
a good oppening hand is if you have preparations, otherwise mulligan.<br />
When you have played gorn and prep., you will not give a lot to your adv. and you should kill his minion before fighting with slaked thirst and other wounding cards.<br />
<br />
the shadow that could kill you is gollum ninja.<br />
Against that deck, you should survive and try to kill him, so no double move and kill lego and don&#39;t play anything before. Then he can&#39;t play gollum + shelob before site 7!<br />
<br />
Your shadow is awful and is a killing machine when someone is in the dead pile!<br />
